title: EP.34: POST DRAFT ANALYSIS, WALKER OVER HUTCHINSON, DRAFT DAY TRADES, NBA PLAYOFFS ROUND 2, AND MUCH MORE!
description: In this episode we do a deep dive into the 2022 NFL Draft and analyze some of the picks and huge trades that were made. Who had the best draft? Which team got a whole lot better? Who ya got in the second round of the NBA playoffs? Tune in and find out!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
